      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 14:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三天内两次震荡令健康险投资者措手不及</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/elevance-tumbles-on-forecast-cut-third-quarter-earnings-miss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的健康保险公司在三天内两次下调盈利预测，令投资者大吃一惊，导致股价暴跌 — — 华尔街不禁想知道未来是否还会有更多意外情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/elevance-tumbles-on-forecast-cut-third-quarter-earnings-miss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:17:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
