      <title>交易员权衡美国库存下降和中国刺激措施 油价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-17</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡美国原油库存下降、中东生产的潜在风险与中国刺激措施的力度不够等因素，油价出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-17</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 23:29:45 GMT</pubDate>
